            "body": "This should absolutely be using the dev-support/docker/Dockerfile and not something custom.  As it stands, this Dockerfile is missing some absolutely critical parts (eg, everything native) and is downloading components that are very different than what the ASF actually uses for its tests. (Why is maven coming from Fedora instead of, you know, Apache?)",
